reviewText: This dvd was good! Two of the comedians weren't that funny to me but the other five were funny, so I don't feel like I wasted my money. And one of the comedians son was given a chance to shine and he was funny too. So there was a total of 8 stand-up acts. Jamie Foxx didn't really bring any "funny" in my opinion but he was a good host. All in all, it was worth the purchase.
I love this comedy standup series. Movie plays well, and I will be ordering more. Thanks! I watch this very often!

Very funny. I have been laughing for a month. Jamie foxx is a fool,this is the best comedy show I
Seen in a long time.
